pSybq240D7EaN2P1EwpyY4QA7TS3s3yrkf7fKMH6QPumYZ6OWhSWeYcGPH5qS1cPirf3gFE8aIB)\\n\\nOr maybe, you just want to peruse through all of our Wedding Planning Tips. (https://be324.keap-link017.com/v2/click/db1c9999947d7b05d1ba579706f/eJyNUV1rwkAQ_C8H9cmYDxUhEIqIlaD1obTPcsktcel9cbexDeJ_7522PrXQt2NmdnZm78wINNdUC1ayBqbFjI2ZgxYtgqaV0cTbK5lni2yej5lE_b5xpresPP82e-cjOi_y-ZjRYCEoXl-Wq2293xx29X4blJa7sOI_NtNFkRXTu9H6eVnv2OXypzMopPUpmHtWkushNhIYWtGbk0F_JLK-TNNGmm7yAYLgk_ykNSptOUFn3JAGVKDuEiu51vFBaH362JM6eNO7FioJXCQSPSUtV5Zjp0eRVWFTrypQHOUV-GEr1MK0h1OW3-Bw2pCwaowYkhhgtI4jFZcS-RF6Dw2ah1nWRTRmGz2h87TnCqrlVROKcmtBi-9f2sJwq3v5AiX9oQk=)\\n\\nThe WedTexts blog is jam packed with great information to make your wedding planning easier and make your wedding a memorable experience for everyone!\\n\\nOh wait, do you have questions about the WedTexts app?\\n\\nWe’ve got a blog for that too!\\n\\nClick here to see answers to all the WedTexts FAQs. (https://be324.keap-link017.com/v2/click/ff441239e80d0dcc838e255245e0c466/eJyNUUtrwkAQ_i8L9eSah4oQCCWIlaD1UNqzbLLTZOm-ujvRivjfu4nVUwu9fq_5ZuZMEDTTWHKSkQqm6YyMiYNaWAEal0YjqwcyiRfxPBkTKfTH2pnOkuz8m_fO9-g8TRZjgicLQfH6Uiw35W6935a7TVBa5sKI_8RMF2mcTu9Bq-ei3JLL5c9kUAJXhxDuSYaug34jLsJW-OZk0LeI1mdRVEnTTI7AEb7QT2qjomPLkIZeNKBc6Ib2FFXgPWvAU6Y5NdiCozcXfWefPnrsUO296VwNuQTGqRQeac2UZaLRo55VoUGnclBMyAG4sbnQ3NT7Q5xc4XDy0DyvDD8N00er3pIzKQVrofNQCfMwi5se7TuPnoTzuGMK8mLQhAMwa0Hzn-9t4HQ9w-UblFKp9g==)\\n\\nHave any other questions?\\n\\nReply to this email and let me know what questions you need answered to make sure your wedding planning is effective and enjoyable.\\n\\nTalk soon!\",\n  \"path\": \"memory/19006594.md\"\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# Ticket #19006594\n\n**Subject:** Re: Built to answer your burning questions\n\n**Created:** 2024-06-29T20:50:13Z\n\n## Description\n\nHello can I get a refund because my wedding is in mexico and Wedtexts isnt guaranteed to work there?\n\nOn Jun 29, 2024, at 6:01 AM, WedTexts <xxxxx@xxxxx.xxx> wrote:\n\n﻿\nHey Alliah, How crazy was yesterday’s wedding horror story?! If you want to read more stories like that one and posts by real\n\nHey Alliah,\n\nHow crazy was yesterday’s wedding horror story?!\n\nIf you want to read more stories like that one and posts by real wedding couples who’ve used WedTexts, you can find more here on our blog. (https://be324.keap-link017.com/v2/click/a9be9a0a7b9f752a0cb73e6bf7da5d94/eJyNUV1rwjAU_S-B-WRt6wdioYwiTorOh7E9S5pcali-SG7divjfl-j0ycHewjnnnnPPzYkgaKqx5qQgDUzGUzIkDpiwAjQujUbKLmSezbNZPiRS6M-1M50lxenR7J2P6CxfLIYEewtB8f5WLTf1br3f1rtNUFrqQsR_bCbzcTae3I1Wr1W9Jefzn86gBK6OwdyTAl0HsREXoRV-OBn0B0TrizRtpGlHX8ARvtGPmFEpowitcX3qgMrkRsUHF7r16XOHau9N5xiUEihPpPCYMKosFa0eRFaFqE6VoKiQF-DGlkJzw_bHLL_C4bZhxbIxvE9izGAVR0oqpaAH6Dw0wjxNszaicbnBi3Aed1RBWV00oSm1FjT__aYN9Ne-5x_m8qGM)\n\nSpeaking of our blog!\n\nOur blog is built to answer your questions, like:\n\nHow do I create my wedding budget? (https://be324.keap-link017.com/v2/click/87c10d1e32d75c46e358d3405ded0d16/eJyNUV1rwjAU_S-B-WRsrYpQKEPESdH5MLZnSZNLDcsX6Y2uiP99iW4-Odjr-brnJGeCYJjBWpCSNDAppmRIPHDpJBhcWoOMX8lxPs9n4yFR0nyuvQ2OlOdH3juf0FmRRwv2DqLi_W2x3NS79X5b7zZR6ZiPJ_4TM5kXeTG5B61eF_WWXC5_JoOWuDrG8I6U6AOkRULGVfjhVdQfEF1XZlmjbDs6gUD4wm7Erc4O9kTRUu6BIdDeBk8jL6RpaRNEC5g9B9T7LhIcKgVMUCU7pJxpx2RrBonV8VjQFWgm1RX4ZStphOX7Yz6-wfF1Y8mqsaKnqcNglSwVU0qyA4QOGmmfpnmb0FRv8CJ9hzumoVpcNXErcw6M-PmoDfS3xZdvyHih1g==)\n\nHow can I make my wedding guest book unique? (https://be324.keap-link017.com/v2/click/ae8a54cdc880433ec7ccf2d33fa4429e/eJyNUV1rwkAQ_C8H9SkxMSpCIBQRK0HrQ2mf5ZJb4uJ99W7PVsT_3ov246WFvs7Mzs7snhmB5ppqwUrWwLiYsIQ5aNEiaFoYTby9kqN8lk9HCZOoDytngmXl-bfZb75Hp0U-ThidLETF89N8sa63q92m3q6j0nIXV_zHZjwr8uLHaPk4rzfscvnTGRTS8hjNPSvJBegbCYyt6MXJqN8TWV9mWSNNN3wDQfBOftgalbUOOOER0qDxNUAaSYG6S7sAntLGmEOKArjP7gOpnTfBtVBJ4CKVGAUtV5Zjpwc9q-LOoCpQHOUV-GIr1MK0u2M-usHxyDFr1RhxSvsog2U_UnEpke8heGjQ3E3yrkf7lIMHdJ62XEE1v2piZW4taPH5rzWcbsUvH20CpKw=)\n\nWhat are the best wedding planning tools to use? (https://be324.keap-link017.com/v2/click/10f6f9dd8e97111042ebc84a49f25