\n\nThe WedTexts blog is jam packed with great information to make your wedding planning easier and make your wedding a memorable experience for everyone!\n\nOh wait, do you have questions about the WedTexts app?\n\nWe’ve got a blog for that too!\n\nClick here to see answers to all the WedTexts FAQs. (https://be324.keap-link017.com/v2/click/ff441239e80d0dcc838e255245e0c466/eJyNUUtrwkAQ_i8L9eSah4oQCCWIlaD1UNqzbLLTZOm-ujvRivjfu4nVUwu9fq_5ZuZMEDTTWHKSkQqm6YyMiYNaWAEal0YjqwcyiRfxPBkTKfTH2pnOkuz8m_fO9-g8TRZjgicLQfH6Uiw35W6935a7TVBa5sKI_8RMF2mcTu9Bq-ei3JLL5c9kUAJXhxDuSYaug34jLsJW-OZk0LeI1mdRVEnTTI7AEb7QT2qjomPLkIZeNKBc6Ib2FFXgPWvAU6Y5NdiCozcXfWefPnrsUO296VwNuQTGqRQeac2UZaLRo55VoUGnclBMyAG4sbnQ3NT7Q5xc4XDy0DyvDD8N00er3pIzKQVrofNQCfMwi5se7TuPnoTzuGMK8mLQhAMwa0Hzn-9t4HQ9w-UblFKp9g==)\n\nHave any other questions?\n\nReply to this email and let me know what questions you need answered to make sure your wedding planning is effective and enjoyable.\n\nTalk soon!","path":"memory/19006594.md"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773116413860}}
{"type":"message","id":"20e029fc","parentId":"f4072970","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:20:21.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Short answer: **yes, but with a caveat.**\n\nWedTexts is only *guaranteed* to work with US cell phone numbers in the US. However, they do have plenty of couples who've used it for Mexico weddings successfully. Here's why it usually works:\n\n- **Most major US carriers** (AT&T, Verizon, T-Mobile) include Mexico & Canada in their plans, so guests with US numbers typically receive texts fine in Mexico.\n- **Anyone with a smartphone on WiFi** can also receive the messages.\n\nThe main risk is if you have guests with non-US numbers or guests on carriers that don't include Mexico roaming.\n\nWorth noting: WedTexts has offered refunds in the past if it doesn't work out for international weddings — so you could ask about that as a safety net when signing up.\n\nWant me to dig into anything else about it?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":197,"cacheRead":13650,"cacheWrite":4169,"totalTokens":18017,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0049250000000000006,"cacheRead":0.0068249999999999995,"cacheWrite":0.02605625,"total":0.03781125}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773116413862}}
