{"type":"message","id":"b538d1af","parentId":"b9bc832a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:20:55.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe info came from these support tickets:\n\n- **Ticket #19006541** — A customer asking about their Mexico City wedding and US carrier coverage\n- **Ticket #19006626** — James (CEO, WedTexts) confirming they have \"a lot of international weddings using WedTexts (including Mexico)\" and offering a post-wedding refund if it doesn't work\n- **Ticket #19006594** — A customer requesting a refund because WedTexts isn't guaranteed for Mexico"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":115,"cacheRead":17819,"cacheWrite":270,"totalTokens":18207,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.002875,"cacheRead":0.008909499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0016875,"total":0.013486999999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773116451459}}
