{"type":"message","id":"7049c9e0","parentId":"62de7908","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:21:34.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nFrom Ticket #19006626, here's the exact quote from James (CEO, WedTexts):\n\n> \"WedTexts is only guaranteed to work in the US with US cell phone numbers.\n> \n> But... with that being said, we do have a lot of international weddings using WedTexts (including Mexico).\n> \n> They do so because most international cell phone plans are able to receive the texts and anyone with a smartphone who is connected to wifi can also receive the messages.\"\n\nAnd regarding the refund offer:\n\n> \"Also, if you want to try WedTexts in Mexico, I'm happy to refund you after your wedding if it doesn't work for some reason.\""}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":158,"cacheRead":18089,"cacheWrite":191,"totalTokens":18441,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00395,"cacheRead":0.0090445,"cacheWrite":0.0011937500000000001,"total":0.01420325}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773116489474}}
